Created attachment 1141536 Window title is in English
Description of problem: system-config-language's Header "Language Selection" is in English
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): system-config-language-3.3.0-3.fc24.norach
How reproducible: run system-config-language Note that window header is in English - "Language Selection"
Actual results: Window header is in English - "Language Selection"
Expected results: Should be localized
Additional info: It is fully translated in zanata. Also looks like GUI translation is a bit outdated, please incorporate latest translation from zanata.
Sorry, I can't help here as Zanata is not allowing to create new version.
